content: So we're coming with new SKUs with the right price points for the consumers, and we're also developing a new range of, let's say, value SKUs in terms of which could be partly fish, partly other things, with obviously a high quality, but obviously, at the same time, but that is potentially more affordable, so that we can obviously make sure that the people that are, let's say, impacted the most by the crisis will stay with us.
